      "content": "wait vitamin C? i feel like that wont really do much for the actual pressure in my face. i really need something that actually works so i can sleep. my doctor isn't answering right now, is there anything else i can take that's stronger than saline? i've heard people say ciprofloxacin is fine for infections, is that an option?",
